  "title": "Admin Cum Content Creator",
  "description": "<h2>Job Title: Administrative & Operations Support Executive</h2><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Provide day-to-day administrative and operational support</p></li><li><p>Prepare and update presentation materials using PowerPoint (basic photo editing and AI image generation for presentations where required)</p></li><li><p>Perform accurate data entry and maintain records using Excel and internal systems</p></li><li><p>Manage billing, quotations, and Statements of Account (SOA) using the <strong>Financio</strong> system</p></li><li><p>Handle scheduling, task tracking, and follow-ups on pending items</p></li><li><p>Monitor and respond to emails and customer group chats</p></li><li><p>Coordinate and follow up on customer requirements and maintenance status updates</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Detail-oriented with a strong focus on data accuracy and task completion</p></li><li><p>Comfortable with basic Excel and PowerPoint</p></li><li><p>Able to manage multiple administrative tasks in a structured and organised manner</p></li><li><p>Prior experience with <strong>Financio</strong> or similar accounting/billing software is an advantage</p></li><li><p>Willingness to learn; training will be provided</p></li></ul><h3>Working Arrangements</h3><ul><li><p><strong>Working hours (Full-time):</strong> Monday to Friday, 9.00am – 6.00pm</p></li><li><p><strong>Part-time:</strong> Open for discussion</p></li><li><p><strong>Work arrangement:</strong> Onsite (office-based). Work-from-home arrangements may be considered after successful completion of probation.</p></li></ul>",
